      <scopecontent id="aspace_9157ace1137e92947bdf0c2a6d9425d7">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of membership lists, charter, printed matter, news articles, and notes documenting the activities and operations of the Korean American Students of Yale (KASY), an undergraduate Yale organization. Also included are the rcords of the Korean-American Intercollegiate Network (KIN).</p>  
